headline: S&P Global Selects Linde for Sustainability Yearbook 2025
summary: WOKING, England, April 22, 2025--Linde plc (Nasdaq: LIN) announced today that it has been recognized for its industry-leading sustainability performance through inclusion in the S&P Global Sustainability Yearbook 2025.
